The JSON Convert demo wiki ships two long-form guides:

* [[Profile Guide]] -- what a profile is, anatomy, building one by hand or with the editor.
* [[Console Guide]] -- the Console workflow end to end: loading source, picking a profile, converting, reviewing the staging area, applying.

For the full reference -- recipes, error codes, plugin internals -- see the [[Usage guide|$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage]] in the plugin itself.

Each guide is structured the same way: every chapter and section is its own tiddler under the guide entry in the sidebar.  Open a section to read just that piece; open the guide tiddler to read the whole thing top-to-bottom (chapters and sub-sections are transcluded inline).
